OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FA rather
OL,6,Fcloudy evening with further showers,
OL,7,Fthese focused across the north. Clear
OL,8,Fspells developing overnight,
OL,9,Fparticularly in the Central Belt where
OL,10,Fshowers die out.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSunday:FMost enjoying a dry day with
OL,13,Fgood sunny spells and light winds,
OL,14,Fwith the Central Belt particularly
OL,15,Ffavoured and warm. However, some early
OL,16,Fshowers possible in the far north.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
